# Environment variables for Matrix-New
# DO NOT commit real tokens into the repository.

# GitHub token used by your website server to fetch release assets from private repos
# Example name: GITHUB_DOWNLOAD_TOKEN
# Set this on your hosting platform or server as an environment variable.
GITHUB_DOWNLOAD_TOKEN=

# EAS credentials are usually kept in your local environment or CI provider.
# See EAS docs for configuring `eas.json` and auth: https://docs.expo.dev/eas/
